      <h1>The Philosophy of Financial Freedom: What It Really Means and Why It Matters</h1>
      <p class="article-subtitle">Financial freedom is not about being rich — it is about having enough options to live on your own terms. Explore the philosophy behind genuine financial independence beyond just the numbers.</p>
